---
title: Chargrilled Chicken & Chipotle Bacon Nachos with Capsicum & Avocado Salad
description: We recommend saving some room during the day because you’re going to need a lot of space for this truck load of flavour.
A Tex-Mex spiced chicken, charred golden on the BBQ is irresistible so we’re providing you with half a chicken to ensure everyone gets a bite. Try eating it with the bacon and cheese nachos, with a chipotle sauce to really get the party started.
